/* ─── Standalone URL /dinoco-sn-golive/ (V.1.2) ─────────────────
 *
 * Hook template_redirect → intercept URL → render raw HTML page
 * (full DOCTYPE + html + head + body). Bypasses theme + Elementor +
 * header/footer entirely. Same auth gate as shortcode.
 *
 * Boss directive 2026-05-15: "ทำหน้าแยกแบบนี้ดีกว่าอย่าไปยุ่ง wp"
 *
 * URL: https://dinoco.in.th/dinoco-sn-golive/
